    "instruction": "Load log.csv and parse timestamps to UTC. Compute global P95 for each (cmdb_id, log_name) across the full series (do NOT filter by the incident window). Then filter log rows to the incident window 2024-01-24 01:15:03 UTC — 2024-01-24 01:45:03 UTC. Restrict analysis to these services: ts-order-service, ts-station-service, ts-inside-payment-service, ts-travel-service, ts-train-service, ts-auth-service. For each (cmdb_id, log_name) return: cmdb_id, log_name, total_points_in_window, global_p95, in_window_mean, in_window_max, count_in_window_ge_p95, earliest_timestamp_in_window_ge_p95 (UTC ISO, null if none). Only return rows where count_in_window_ge_p95 > 0. Limit output to top 20 rows sorted by count_in_window_ge_p95 desc then in_window_max desc. Keep output compact (no raw series)."
}

